、他のアイドルと戦うの？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"area4686-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"ええ、新人アイドルを集めてのトーナメント戦。\n司会が有名芸人なこともあって、毎年そこそこの注目度の番組よ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"area4686-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"イヴ","body":"みなさんと、和服を着てのお仕事……\nとても楽しみです！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"area4686-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"そう！　だけど楽しみなのは、それだけじゃないんだよ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"area4686-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"麻弥","body":"彩さん、どうしたんですか？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"area4686-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"『ガチバトル！　ユニット対抗アイドル百人一首大会！』で\n優勝したアイドルユニットは、その年ブレイクするって\nジンクスがあるんだ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"area4686-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"千聖","body":"そう。来年のパスパレのさらなる飛躍のために、\n絶対に優勝しましょうね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"area4686-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"日菜","body":"んー。ジンクスとかはよくわかんないけど……\nどうせやるなら勝ちたいし、みんなで優勝目指そっか♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"area4686-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"イヴ","body":"はい！\n勝負は正々堂々、勝ちにいくのがブシドーです！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId